
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Results - There's Something About AI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/results.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                    <div class="logo-icon">AI</div>
                    <h1 class="logo-text">There's Something About AI</h1>
                </a>
                <nav class="nav">
                    <a href="index.html" class="nav-link">Home</a>
                    <a href="instructions.html" class="nav-link">Instructions</a>
                    <a href="about.html" class="nav-link">About</a>
                    <a href="roadmap.html" class="nav-link">Roadmap</a>
                    <a href="profile.html" class="nav-link profile-link">Profile</a>
                </nav>
                <button class="mobile-menu-btn" id="mobileMenuBtn">☰</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Results Section -->
    <main class="main">
        <section class="results-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="results-header">
                    <h1>AI Response Comparison</h1>
                    <div class="prompt-display">
                        <strong>Your Prompt:</strong>
                        <span id="displayPrompt">Loading...</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Comparison Controls -->
                <div class="comparison-controls">
                    <button class="compare-btn active" data-compare="1-2">Compare AI 1 vs AI 2</button>
                    <button class="compare-btn" data-compare="1-3">Compare AI 1 vs AI 3</button>
                    <button class="compare-btn" data-compare="2-3">Compare AI 2 vs AI 3</button>
                    <button class="compare-btn" data-compare="all">Show All</button>
                </div>

                <!-- AI Responses Grid -->
                <div class="responses-grid" id="responsesGrid">
                    <div class="response-card" data-ai="1">
                        <div class="response-header">
                            <h3>GPT-4</h3>
                            <span class="ai-badge">AI Engine 1</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="response-content" id="response1">
                            <p>This is a sample response from GPT-4. It provides comprehensive analysis with detailed explanations and examples. The response demonstrates strong reasoning capabilities and covers multiple aspects of the query with high accuracy and relevance.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="response-card" data-ai="2">
                        <div class="response-header">
                            <h3>Claude</h3>
                            <span class="ai-badge">AI Engine 2</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="response-content" id="response2">
                            <p>Claude's response focuses on structured analysis and ethical considerations. It offers a different perspective with emphasis on practical applications and potential limitations. The approach is methodical and includes relevant context.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="response-card" data-ai="3">
                        <div class="response-header">
                            <h3>Gemini</h3>
                            <span class="ai-badge">AI Engine 3</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="response-content" id="response3">
                            <p>Gemini provides a concise yet informative response with focus on key insights. The answer is well-structured and includes specific examples that illustrate the main points effectively. It balances brevity with comprehensiveness.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Differences Display -->
                <div class="differences-section">
                    <h2>Key Differences</h2>
                    <div class="differences-content" id="differencesContent">
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <strong>Approach:</strong> GPT-4 focuses on comprehensive analysis, Claude emphasizes ethical considerations, while Gemini provides concise insights.
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <strong>Detail Level:</strong> GPT-4 offers extensive detail, Claude provides structured analysis, Gemini balances brevity with depth.
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <strong>Perspective:</strong> Each AI brings unique viewpoints to the same query, demonstrating diverse analytical approaches.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- New Prompt Section -->
        <section class="new-prompt-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="prompt-card">
                    <div class="prompt-header">
                        <h2>Try Another Prompt</h2>
                        <div class="history-dropdown">
                            <button class="history-btn" id="historyBtn">History ▼</button>
                            <div class="history-menu" id="historyMenu">
                                <div class="history-item">Previous prompt 1...</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <textarea 
                        class="prompt-input" 
                        id="promptInput"
                        placeholder="Type your next prompt here..."
                        rows="4"
                    ></textarea>
                    <button class="submit-btn" id="submitBtn">Compare AI Responses</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <h3>There's Something About AI</h3>
                <p>Compare and analyze GenAI responses with sophisticated semantic analysis</p>
                <div class="footer-bottom">
                    <p>© 2024 There's Something About AI. All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="js/results.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
